{"tid":1327780,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂] 野餐零食圖文攻略！！","createTime":"2019-07-17T17:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T00:58:59.000Z","uid":238696,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c837719b1b2460fb9fd5e4e0224783850926f2a1","tid":1327780,"uid":238696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:20:42.000Z","msg":"咁多物資裝備post，但係好似冇咩人講後援嘅零食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果果日係由朝到晚嘅話（好似71咁），補充體力好緊要，因為可以連飯都唔得閒食！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係唔好亂買，否則只會造成物資站負荷過大同浪費</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宜✅ ：</span><br />\n<br />\n獨立包裝梳打餅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmLxg9O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmLxg9O.png&h=0a0a18a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n細細包嘅零食先多人攞<br />\n<br />\n得力素<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrCPjok.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrCPjok.png&h=a6fe0efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葡萄糖醒腦，補充維他命c<br />\n<br />\n蕉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqO3oQh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqO3oQh.png&h=3c90a2ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係講笑，最多人拎，次次都最快清哂<br />\n<br />\n寶礦力<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mu9RxLH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMu9RxLH.png&h=f7a970ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔使解釋啦<br />\n<br />\nBonaqua<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wyGgJSy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwyGgJSy.png&h=d6ac6e8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太古集團<br />\n<br />\n津路<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSMDXaG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSMDXaG.png&h=82ef760e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係隔離post見到，中椒中蛋可以用嚟洗眼（有待考證？）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322657\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322657</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可以買，但盡量唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：</span><br />\n<br />\n三文治、有餡嘅包（例如 腸仔包 奶黃包 麥當勞包）<br />\n唔擺得耐，天氣熱好易變壞，食到成手汁會唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n朱古力/energy bar<br />\n溶左通常都冇人想食<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">忌❌：</span><br />\n<br />\n薯片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n花生/一大包韓國腰果果仁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n年輪蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係見過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 港島見！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 港島見！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721 港島見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n集中返 五大訴求 + 社會信用評分 + 監控燈柱<br />\n<br />\n不受傷 不被捕 不分化 不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家<br />\n香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd2cb5623424d6214aebc590cb5589e74461353","tid":1327780,"uid":175870,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:25:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻一阻你<br />\n鑒於太多人搞錯物資手勢要再宣傳下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再搞錯索帶同長遮手勢</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oz18Aaq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foz18Aaq.png&h=357e25fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"p